# Place convention photos here for bulk upload.
#
# Folder structure:
#   gallery-import/
#     2025/
#       photo-01.jpg
#       photo-02.jpg
#     2024/
#       ...
#
# Before running npm run upload-gallery:
# 1. Create matching gallery albums in Admin → Galleries
# 2. Set IMPORT_SECRET in Convex dashboard and .env.local
# 3. Run: npm run upload-gallery
